libaiff
------------------------------------------
Open-source implementation of the AIFF format

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libaiff-devel-6.0-1bl1
  libaiff2-6.0-1bl1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-3
  autoconf-archive-2024.10.16-1
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-14.4.0-1
  libtool-2.5.4-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/mtszb/libaiff

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/mtszb/libaiff/archive/refs/tags/v6.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libaiff-6.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libaiff-6.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libaiff-6.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libaiff-6.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libaiff2-6.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libaiff-devel-6.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libaiff)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libaiff.README
  /usr/share/doc/libaiff/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/libaiff/README

(libaiff2)
  /usr/bin/cygaiff-2.dll

(libaiff-devel)
  /usr/include/libaiff/config.h
  /usr/include/libaiff/endian.h
  /usr/include/libaiff/libaiff.h
  /usr/lib/libaiff.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libaiff.pc

------------------

